And from my perspective, the price is reasonable and within the standard Barbie setrange. And this set goes with other Barbie collection and my girls it is a great mix and match.General speaking, a happy purchase. I would love to recommend it as a holiday gift set orpresent to girls. Good "old school" fun

LayoutNode.Content: I got this for my little cousin, who loves Barbies. While I didn't play with Barbies myself when Iwas younger, it's nice to see toys from my childhood still being enjoyed by the youth of today(you know, when they're not on their iPads). Most of the time I see her, she's playing Minecraftor some other mobile game, so it's refreshing to see her play with actual tangible toys like I didwhen I was younger. That it contends with her electronic devices speaks for itself in theentertainment value of this set. I will say on the downside, the pieces are small and she'salready lost a few pieces. I also feel like maybe it should have come with at least one Barbiecharacter rather than having to buy one separately. Otherwise, it seems to be good wholesomefun for my cousin. I received this product at a discounted price in return for my unbiasedreview. See more

Fun cabin set

LayoutNode.Content: I love this cabin set. I recently bought this for my cousin and she absolutely loves it. The cabinset comes with built-in kitchen appliances, sofa, table, two chairs, and a very cute puppy. Thisis a perfect addition to her Barbie camping collection. She has two camping dolls and lovesplaying with this set. Every detail in this set is so thought about. The two story cabin home hasa beautiful room with kitchen, fireplace, tv and a chandelier. She likes to play cooking in thekitchen as if you were camping in real world. The camping dolls even have a puppy to play with.What I really like is you can rearrange the furniture in the cabin, this gives a different look eachtime you play. . Such a perfect cabin set to play with. Overall I really like the set and highlyrecommend. I received this product at a discounted price in return for my unbiased review. See more

Cabin Fever Fun

LayoutNode.Content: Because we have been having very rainy days, my daughter hasn't been able to go outside toplay. While she has already put in her request to go camping, we had to tell her that it isn'tcamping time just yet. While I can't reward her with camping at this time, upon seeing this set, Iknew I could provide her with a taste. Seriously, this cabin is equipped with everything,including a hot chocolate maker! So far, we have had a tea party and a sleepover! The doggieis a nice addition, but he could use a bed. Currently, my daughter has him sleeping in thefireplace (of course, she reminded me that the fire is off). We purchased two other Barbiecamping dolls, which greatly add to the fun. I received this product at a discounted price inreturn for my unbiased review.” See more

LayoutNode.SRC: Great addition to First Barbie Doll

LayoutNode.Content: I got it at a discount in exchange for review. If you are to buy your first barbie for your child, thedoll itself will be boring without this house. This is the next best thing to those giant doll house.And much more affordable. All the little pieces are nicely detailed. I like how the pieces attachesto table and doesn't slide off easily. She can play in in the car and long drives. My 4 year oldplays tea time with this set and I'm a bit surprised she even knows tea time at this age. 4 starsbecause one of the walls is just cardboard paper. If it gets wet, you can either print a new wallor color one. Else it'd be 5 stars. See more
